<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog Post Card</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="blog-post-card">
     <img
      class="post-img"
      src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/cover-photo.jpg"
      alt="Cover photo for the blog post">
        <div class="post-content">
      <h2 class="post-title">Getting Started with Web Development</h2>

      <p class="post-excerpt">
        Learn the fundamentals of HTML and CSS to begin building beautiful,
        responsive websites from scratch.
      </p>

      <a class="read-more" href="https://www.freecodecamp.org" target="_blank">
        Read More
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
